          "text": "I just built a Job Hunting Agent, a YouTube to LinkedIn Post agent, & 27+ more AI agents using Scrapingdog 🤯\n\nHere’s how I built the YouTube Shorts–to–LinkedIn Post agent:\n\n1) A YouTube Shorts link is added to Google Sheets.\n2) N8N picks it up using a scheduled trigger.\n3) The workflow extracts the video ID from the Shorts URL.\n4) Scrapingdog pulls the full transcript of the Short via its YouTube Transcript API.\n5) The transcript chunks are aggregated into one clean block of text.\n6) An AI node rewrites the transcript into a LinkedIn-style post.\n7) The post is published on LinkedIn.\n8) The live LinkedIn URL is written back to Google Sheets.\n\nThe result:\nOne YouTube Short automatically becomes a LinkedIn post\n\nAll you need to run this is access to Scrapingdog’s API, n8n, and a Google Sheet.\n\nI’ve also created a doc showing how you can build 27+ more no-code AI agents using Scrapingdog.\n\nJust comment “agent” and I’ll DM you.",
